widgets_values: Claire Hemmings, an 18-year-old honors graduate from Des Moines, Iowa, seated at a round black-painted table on the outdoor patio of a classical-style cafÃ© during early evening. She has light skin tone with natural coloration, light blonde hair tied back neatly, and wears clear round eyeglasses. She is smiling gently, holding a partially finished cocktail glass in her left hand, which rests casually on the table. She wears a light pink graphic T-shirt under an oversized olive-green utility jacket, and beige shorts. A blue smartwatch is visible on her left wrist. The table shows signs of wear with paint chipped at the edge. Behind her is a large white column with soft yellow artificial lighting cast upward. The setting includes deep red patio flooring, woven rattan chairs with red-and-black pattern, green plants, and a backdrop of historic brick buildings partially obscured by large trees with dense foliage. The ambient lighting is dim, indicating dusk, with bluish sky visible through the canopy. The camera captures her from a slightly low, front-facing angle at medium close-up range, emphasizing the warm, relaxed atmosphere and architectural details in the background.
